{"tid":112931,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"那夜凌晨我拖了女神的手","createTime":"2017-02-08T14:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T15:15:35.000Z","uid":42755,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf207aec82926932be2da516f3a8b78dcad1a784","tid":112931,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"長長的秀髮，瓜子口臉，大大圓圓的雙眼，白哲勝雪的肌膚。天女下凡？當我回過神來的時候，原來同女神同班。<br />\n<br />\n女神叫黃婉玲，係呢班男女比例差唔多一比一既班級度，其實真係屬於最頂尖既一、兩個靚女。<br />\n<br />\n為左接近女神，我日日搵啲無聊話題同女神搭訕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 小玲，今日物理堂份功課應該點做架？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咪咁咁咁囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 不如妳俾電話我今晚再問妳吖？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 咁煩架，好啦。9123 4567<br />\n<br />\n(小玲成績好，問功課呢個藉口實無死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n拎到女神電話，搞掂<br />\n<br />\n(頭盔: 真人假事改編，如有雷同，純屬雷同)"},{"pid":"695871a29536390a63bed6bedb1ef15e8080fc31","tid":112931,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:20:06.000Z","msg":"F5"},{"pid":"d12864dee27ecd15d3b4f78616e4c31519c32d63","tid":112931,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:28:05.000Z","msg":"返到屋企正諗住打俾女神既時候，「的搭」既訊息聲響起，當堂嚇一跳，毒撚平時無人搵，第一次聽到預設既訊息鈴聲，開頭仲以為咩事。<br />\n<br />\n「黃婉玲」電話屏幕上顯示既係女神個名。<br />\n<br />\n女神竟然搵我？！一睇就出事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 阿樂，我份物理功課漏左係學校吖，今日教你唔到啦。<br />\n<br />\n可憐天下毒撚心，同女神第一次既訊息就係請我食檸檬！？<br />\n<br />\n唔通女神咁唔想我打俾佢！？"},{"pid":"d1f5ee48524f62f3784b0cd8f5842ab0815243e5","tid":112931,"uid":42755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"預感爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2cc35eea72674c2a00981e46a08a35eb24b143","tid":112931,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:02:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返到屋企正諗住打俾女神既時候，「的搭」既訊息聲響起，當堂嚇一跳，毒撚平時無人搵，第一次聽到預設既訊息鈴聲，開頭仲以為咩事。<br />\n<br />\n「黃婉玲」電話屏幕上顯示既係女神個名。<br />\n<br />\n女神竟然搵我？！一睇就出事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 阿樂，我份物理功課漏左係學校吖，今日教你唔到啦。<br />\n<br />\n可憐天下毒撚心，同女神第一次既訊息就係請我食檸檬！？<br />\n<br />\n唔通女神咁唔想我打俾佢！？</blockquote><br />\n唔可以參軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8c00d740599e6e0f7859b696b5a423b4c94321","tid":112931,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"得我一個回你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32172e94af128a98e358de7b7f48e5b9acd7a4f4","tid":112931,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1845cb41373258f5ef842851258e91add3179337","tid":112931,"uid":47860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"繼續"}]}